{"lemma":"حَدِيدُ","slug":"حَدِيدُ","root":"ح.د.د","root_slug":"ح-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-د-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَدِيد","root":"حدد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":6},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7279"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%AF%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"armor, helmet"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"iron","tags":["uncountable"],"examples":[{"text":"لَقَدْ أَرْسَلْنَا رُسُلَنَا بِالْبَيِّنَاتِ وَأَنزَلْنَا مَعَهُمُ الْكِتَابَ وَالْمِيزَانَ لِيَقُومَ النَّاسُ بِالْقِسْطِ وَأَنزَلْنَا الْحَدِيدَ فِيهِ بَأْسٌ شَدِيدٌ وَمَنَافِعُ لِلنَّاسِ وَلِيَعْلَمَ اللَّهُ مَن يَنصُرُهُ وَرُسُلَهُ بِالْغَيْبِ إِنَّ اللَّهَ قَوِيٌّ عَزِيزٌ.","english":"We have already sent Our messengers with clear evidences and sent down with them the Scripture and the balance that the people may maintain [their affairs] in justice. And We sent down iron, wherein is great military might and benefits for the people, and so that Allah may make evident those who support Him and His messengers unseen. Indeed, Allah is Powerful and Exalted in Might."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħa.diːd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7279","headword_ar":"حَدِيدٌ","root":"Hd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAd~N","text_ar":"مُحَادٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Hadiydu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ حَدِيدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is the close,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next, neighbour of such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning that the house of the former is next by the side of that of the latter; (A, * L;) or that the land of the former is adjacent to that of the latter. (S, L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa HadydiY","text_ar":"هُوَ حَديدِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Ald~aAri","text_ar":"فِى الدَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAd~iY","text_ar":"مُحَادِّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is my next neighbour in respect of house"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAriY Hadiydapu daArihi","text_ar":"دَارِى حَدِيدَةُ دَارِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAd~atuhaA","text_ar":"مُحَادَّتُهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lidaArihi","text_ar":"لِدَارِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHAd~apN","text_ar":"مُحادَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My house is close,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjoining, to his house;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning that the limit of the former is like that of the latter. (L, K. *)       -A2-  Also, (S, L, Msb, K,) used as masc. and fem. without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and also as fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAd~N","text_ar":"حَادٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, Msb,) but this is disapproved by IKh, (TA,) though allowed by some as agreeable with analogy, (MF,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HudaAdN","text_ar":"حُدَادٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, L, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hud~aAdN","text_ar":"حُدَّادٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, S, L, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Edged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharpened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a sword, (S, Msb,) a knife, (L, Msb, K,) [and the like: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp-pointed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl. [of the first]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HidaAdN","text_ar":"حِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) masc. and fem.; (L;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydaAtN","text_ar":"حَدِيدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAy^idu","text_ar":"حَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) fem. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAbN HadiydN","text_ar":"نَابٌ حَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydapN","text_ar":"حَدِيدَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sharp canine tooth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HudaAdN","text_ar":"حُدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus applied has not been heard. (L.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN HadiydN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ حَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who is sharp"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effective"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of eloquence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of intellect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHotad~N","text_ar":"مُحْتَدٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of anger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHid~aA=hu","text_ar":"اَحِدَّا=هُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHid~apN","text_ar":"اَحِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HidaAdN","text_ar":"حِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alosinapN HidaAdN","text_ar":"اَلْسِنَةٌ حِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharp tongues."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN Hadiydu Aln~aAZiri","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ حَدِيدُ النَّاظِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who looks sharply,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boldly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man not suspected of evil, so that he should cast down his eyes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fabaSaruka Alyawoma","text_ar":"فَبَصَرُكَ اليَوْمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydN","text_ar":"حَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the Kur 1. 21] means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And thy sight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intellect, to-day, is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piercing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that thou perceivest therewith what thou didst not know, or what thou deemedst improbable, in thy life on earth: (Jel:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy judgment, to-day, is penetrating."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iHapN HadiydapN","text_ar":"رَايِحَةٌ حَدِيدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAd~apN","text_ar":"حَادَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sharp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pungent, odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN Hadiydapu Aljir~api","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ حَدِيدَةُ الجِرَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel whose cud has a pungent odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) which is a quality approved. (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydN","text_ar":"حَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Iron;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain substance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;) so called because of its resistance: (S, L:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydapN","text_ar":"حَدِيدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a more particular term, (S,) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an instrument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implement, thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAy^idu","text_ar":"حَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAy^idaAtN","text_ar":"حَدَايِدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S L;) the latter (which is erroneously written in the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydaAtN","text_ar":"حَدِيدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA) is a pl. pl., (L,) sometimes occurring in poetry. (S.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_in~a AlHadiyda biAlHadiydi yufolaHu"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily iron with iron is cloven,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"flH","text_ar":"فلح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And in another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taDoribu fiY HadiydK","text_ar":"تَضْرِبُ فِى حَدِيدٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAridK","text_ar":"بَارِدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou beatest upon cold iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: applied in relation to him who hopes for that of which the attainment is remote, or improbable; and to him in whom is nothing to be hoped for. (Har p. 633.) ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Like iron in hardness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied in this sense to solid hoofs. (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["L","K","A","S","Msb","TA","MF","As","AA","Jel"]}]}}